You can define own functions/methods, called "macros".
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
{% macro abc(i) %}{% if i|dummy(3) is array %}{% for k,v in i|dummy(2) %}{{ abc(v) }}{% endfor %}{% else %}{{ i|dummy(1) }}{% endif %}{% endmacro %}{{ abc(a) }}
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
{"a": [1, 2, 3, [4, 5, 6]]}
